{
  "texts": [
    "It is based on the Sparse Mixture of Experts (SMoE) model which is a type of neural network architecture that combines the strengths of both global and local specialization in learning tasks.",
    "These architectures offer a flexible and adaptive framework for capturing intricate patterns in data while maintaining computational efficiency [34].In the same month, September 2023, Salesforce developed XGen-7B [35].",
    "This family of LLMs, trained on the in-house JaxFormer library and public domain data such as databricks-dolly-15k, oasst1, and Baize, is better equipped to handle longer document inputs.",
    "This capability is domain, it incorporates information from different medical question-answering datasets, research, and consumer queries [23].",
    "Flan-PaLM is the instruction-tuned variant of PaLM."
  ]
}